headline: onsemi (ON) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of analog chips maker onsemi (NASDAQ:ON) jumped 3.1% in the morning session after an analyst at Morgan Stanley raised the firm's price target to $54 from $39.

headline: 1 Volatile Stock with Competitive Advantages and 2 We Avoid
summary: Market swings can be tough to stomach, and volatile stocks often experience exaggerated moves in both directions. While many thrive during risk-on environments, many also struggle to maintain investor confidence when the ride gets bumpy.
